Class DecoMN90

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.jdivelog.model.decompression.DecoMN90
All Implemented Interfaces:
DecompressionTable
public class DecoMN90
extends java.lang.Object
implements DecompressionTable

Description: Class in order to implement the french decompression model. It is based on the work made by Volker Holthaus on Deco2000 tables This simulation is simpler than the Deco2000 because there is less possibilities in the MN90 tables

Author:
szdavid
